### US228 - Export route network in standard aviation formats

### LOGIN - run this request first
POST http://localhost:8081/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "backoffice",
  "password": "backoffice123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("token", response.body.token);
%}

###

### US228 - Export route network as GeoJSON
GET http://localhost:8081/api/routes/export/geojson
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/geo+json

###

### US228 - Export route network as KML
GET http://localhost:8081/api/routes/export/kml
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.google-earth.kml+xml

###

### US228 - Export without authentication should return 401/403
GET http://localhost:8081/api/routes/export/geojson

###

### LOGIN as ATCC - does not have permission to export
POST http://localhost:8081/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "atcc",
  "password": "atcc123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("atcc_token", response.body.token);
%}

###

### US228 - Export as ATCC should return 403
GET http://localhost:8081/api/routes/export/geojson
Authorization: Bearer {{atcc_token}}
